dct_title_s: Somerset County, New Jersey wall map 1850
dct_description_sm: Map of northern Somerset County, N.J. showing Bedminster and Bernards Townships and Bernardsville, Far Hills and Peapack-Gladstone Boroughs. Color coded by township. Inset of Somerville, statistical table of acreage, eight drawn illustrations of buildings and description of county.
dct_publisher_sm: Lloyd Van Derveer, Surveyer, Camden N.J.
